name: django-nested-inline
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "django-nested-inline" %}
{% set version = "0.4.0" %}
{% set md5 = "f05f0e03e2cd0e7f2880890478336f30" %}
{% set build = 0 %}

package:
    name: {{ name }}
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    md5: {{ md5 }}
    patches:
        - zipsafe.patch

build:
    number: {{ build }}
    noarch: python
    script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
    host:
        - pip
        - python
        - setuptools
    run:
        - python

test:
    imports:
        - example
        - nested_inline

about:
    home: https://github.com/s-block/django-nested-inline
    license: MIT
    license_file: LICENSE
    summary: Recursive nesting of inline forms for Django Admin

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - kwilcox
